  <brief_title>A Trial of Blunt Needles for the Reduction of Needlestick Injuries During Cesarean Section</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized Trial of Blunt Needles for the Reduction of Needlestick Injuries During Cesarean Section</official_title>
